OL,3,CMan found guilty of attempted murder
OL,4,Cafter pushing postman onto Tube tracks
OL,6,FA man accused of pushing a Tube
OL,7,Fpassenger on to the tracks has been
OL,8,Ffound guilty of attempted murder.
OL,10,FBrwa Shorsh, 24, shoved stranger
OL,11,FTadeusz Potoczek, 61, at Oxford Circus
OL,12,FUnderground station in central London
OL,13,Fon February 3.
OL,15,FMr Potoczek, a postman who was on his
OL,16,Fway home from work, narrowly missed
OL,17,Ftouching the live rail on the
OL,18,Fsouthbound Victoria Line.
