OL,3,CMan found guilty of attempted murder
OL,4,Cafter pushing postman onto Tube tracks
OL,6,FHe was helped back up to the platform
OL,7,Fby another passenger, and the driver
OL,8,Fof an oncoming train has said that "if
OL,9,Fhe had been on the track a few seconds
OL,10,Flater, he would have been killed",
OL,11,FInner London Crown Court heard.
OL,13,FHe was found guilty by a jury after 32
OL,14,Fminutes of deliberations.
OL,16,FMr Justice Kelleher told the
OL,17,Fdefendant: "You have been found guilty
OL,18,Fof attempted murder, which is a very
OL,19,Fserious offence, and a long prison
OL,20,Fsentence will follow."
